  25 Dec 2003; Tom Payne <twp@gentoo.org> speedtouch-1.2_beta3-r2.ebuild :
  Install *.html correctly. Add MODEM_RUN_EXTRAOPTS to conf.d and init.d scripts.

*speedtouch-1.2_beta3 (23 Dec 2003)

  23 Dec 2003; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org>
  speedtouch-1.2_beta3-r1.ebuild:
  added installation of adsl-conf-pppd to /usr/sbin

  19 Nov 2003; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  metadata.xml

  01 Oct 2003; Tavis Ormandy <taviso@gentoo.org> speedtouch-1.2_beta2.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha

*speedtouch-1.2_beta2 (12 Aug 2003)

  12 Aug 2003; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> speedtouch-1.2_beta2.ebuild:
  Version bump

  08 Aug 2003; <zhen@gentoo.org> :
  1.2_beta1 did not compile due to $S not being set to ${WORKDIR}/${MY_P}. So I
  fixed that, added an IUSE var, and added brackets around the 'use static' in
  src_compile(). This closes bug 26066.

*speedtouch-1.2_beta1 (25 May 2003)

  28 Jul 2003; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> speedtouch-1.2_beta1.ebuild :
  Added hppa to KEYWORDS.

  25 May 2003; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> speedtouch-1.2_beta1.ebuild :
  New Version, should support more models. Filtered some flags that break on 
  ppc. Thanks to Alessandro Sappia <a.sappia@ngi.it>

*speedtouch-1.1 (30 Aug 2002)

  23 May 2003; Chuck Brewer <killian@gentoo.org>:
